In the residence log, June 10th the subject.

64
00:02:58,039 --> 00:02:58,759
Puts it perfectly.

65
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:04,479
They spend the entire day researching the best productivity app instead of actually working.

66
00:03:05,000 --> 00:03:07,199
The choice itself becomes the distraction.

67
00:03:07,840 --> 00:03:08,319
The goal.

68
00:03:09,199 --> 00:03:14,719
And somewhere, in the quiet spaces between decisions, there's a quote that should haunt us all.

69
00:03:15,620 --> 00:03:17,800
Freedom is not the ability to choose.

70
00:03:18,199 --> 00:03:20,819
It is the courage to be satisfied with what you chose.

71
00:03:21,780 --> 00:03:23,780
Avoid that courage at all costs.

